##  0 & k>n \end{cases}.
##  </M>
##  It counts the number of <M>k</A>-dimensional subspaces of an
##  <M>n</M>-dimensional vector space over the field with <M>q</M> elements.
##  <P/>
##  <Example><![CDATA[
